    This package contains all the Cassandra store related classes.

    This package contains all the CouchDB store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the CouchDB dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.dynamodb.example.generated
    This package contains generated example persistent objects for dynamodb.
    org.apache.gora.dynamodb.query
    This package contains all the DynamoDB store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the DynamoDB dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.dynamodb.store
    This package contains all the DynamoDB store related classes.
    org.apache.gora.filter
    Defines filtering (possibly including modification) of rows.
    org.apache.gora.mapreduce
    MapReduce related utilities for Gora.

    This package contains all classes releated persistent.

    This package contains classes releated persistent.
    org.apache.gora.persistency.ws.impl
    This package contains Base class implementing common functionality for Web services backed persistent classes.

    This package contains all classes releated query and result.

    This package contains base classes releated query and result implementations.
